title: Check Azure AD Connect Connector
agents: windows
catalog: os/misc
distribution:
author: Marius Rieder <marius.rieder@scs.ch>
license: GPL
description:
 This check monitors the status of the Azure AD Connect connector status.

 The check can be configured via the corresponding WATO rule {Azure AD Connect Connector}

item:
 The Name of the connector and the Sync Profile

inventory:
 One check per connector and sync profile reported in the agent section {<<<win_adsync_connector>>>}.

